---
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import Footer from "@components/Footer.astro";
import GetAppButton from "@components/GetAppButton.astro";
import Page from "@layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page
  title="Box Timer – CrossFit Workout Timer vs. SmartWOD"
  description="A overall comparison of the features and price between Box Timer – CrossFit Workout Timer and the SmartWOD timer."
  url="https://boxtimer.app/box-timer-vs-smartwod/"
  canonical="https://boxtimer.app/box-timer-vs-smartwod/"
>
  <Container innerClass={"flex-col items-center"}>
    <div class="w-full sm:w-9/12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-sans font-bold">
        Box Timer compared to SmartWOD
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-4">Last updated: February 2026</p>
      <p class="py-8">
        Both Box Timer and SmartWOD are great workout timers! You can compare
        both apps down below, but these are some subjective differences to
        consider before choosing.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8">
        Box Timer have a design that looks like the classic timer at a gym, it's
        easy to see the time and the settings are the same ones that you are
        used to.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-24">
        SmartWOD have a more digital design that makes it more like any other
        app on your phone, this could be good if you're not familiar with the
        timers at gyms.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl mb-8 text-center font-sans font-bold">Comparison</h2>
      <table class="w-full overflow-scroll">
        <tr>
          <th class="w-4/12"></th>
          <th class="font-bold pb-8">Box Timer</th>
          <th class="font-bold pb-8">SmartWOD</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="py-6">
            <b class="font-bold">Workouts</b><br />
            AMRAP<br />
            EMOM<br />
            TABATA<br />
            For Time<br />
            Custom Intervals
          </td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700">
            <br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes
          </td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700">
            <br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            Yes<br />
            <span class="text-red-700">No</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="py-6">
            <b class="font-bold">Price</b><br />
          </td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700"> Free</td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-yellow-600"> Free & Paid</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="py-6">
            <b class="font-bold">Ad free</b><br />
          </td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700"> Yes</td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-red-700">No</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="py-6">
            <b class="font-bold">Sound</b><br />
          </td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700"> Yes</td>
          <td class="text-center py-6 text-green-700"> Yes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="py-6">
            <b class="font-bold">Stores previous workout</b><br />
          </td>
          <td class="text-center text-green-700"> Yes</td>
          <td class="text-center text-green-700"> Yes</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p class="mt-16">
        <b>Related:</b>
        <a
          class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
          href="/2026-best-workout-timers-iphone/"
          >Best Workout Timer Apps for iPhone in 2026</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
    <GetAppButton id="get-app-button-compare" outerClass={"mt-24"} />
  </Container>
  <Footer />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Article",
      "headline": "Box Timer compared to SmartWOD",
      "description": "A comparison of the features and price between Box Timer and SmartWOD workout timers for CrossFit and HIIT training.",
      "datePublished": "2024-01-15",
      "dateModified": "2026-02-08",
      "author": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Edvin Lindén",
        "url": "https://edvinlinden.se"
      },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Box Timer",
        "url": "https://boxtimer.app"
      }
    }
  </script>
</Page>
